<div class="comment" id="comment4130">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/458/" target="_top">crane</a><a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20090317033045im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/4130/">#4130</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/11/17 02:15 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/11/17 02:15 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/commonlisp/">
	  Common Lisp
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>CL の format で。もっときれいに書けそうですが。</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>(defun center (str &amp;optional (width 80))
  (let ((margin (- (length str) width)))
    (if (&gt; margin 0)
        (format t &quot;~a&quot; (subseq str (floor (/ margin 2)) (+ width (floor (/ margin 2)))))
      (format t (format nil &quot;~~~a:@&lt;~~a~~&gt;&quot; width) str))))
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
  <div align = "right" class="banner">
	
	<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/4130/addtag/" class="addtag" id="addtag_4130">タグ</a>:
	
	タグなし
	&nbsp;

	
      [<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/commonlisp/">
		Common Lisp
      </a>]
	  
      [<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/4130/download/">
		ダウンロード
      </a>]
