	<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/4160/">#4160</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/11/17 15:45 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/11/17 15:45 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/emacslisp/">
	  Emacs Lisp
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>Emacs Lisp
実行結果:
(string-centering "abc" 0)
""
(string-centering "abc" 1)
"b"
(string-centering "abc" 2)
"ab"
(string-centering "abc" 3)
"abc"
(string-centering "abc" 4)
"abc "
(string-centering "abc" 5)
" abc "
(string-centering "abc" 6)
" abc  "
(string-centering "abc" 7)
"  abc  "</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>(defun string-centering (s c)
  (let ((p (lambda (k) (make-string k ? )))
        (d (- c (length s))))
    (let ((n (/ d 2))
          (m (% d 2)))
      (if (&gt;= d 0)
          (concat (funcall p n) s (funcall p (+ n m)))
        (substring s (abs n) (- (length s) (abs (+ n m))))))))
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
