<div class="comment" id="comment4199">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/415/" target="_top">yohei</a><a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20090317033045im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20090317033045im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/4199/">#4199</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/11/18 08:30 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/11/18 08:30 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/c/">
	  C
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #cfffcf;">3/3=1.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <p>&quot;%.*s&quot; で幅制限出来たのか...
ただ、d &gt; 0 で d が奇数のときに、１桁足りないようです。
それを踏まえて、自分ならこう書きます。</p>

	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
7
8</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="kt">char</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="nf">centering</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">char</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">dest</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">char</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">w</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">d</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">w</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">strlen</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">);</span>
  
  <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">d</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="n">sprintf</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dest</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;%*s%*s&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">w</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">d</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">d</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;&quot;</span><span class="p">);</span>
  <span class="k">else</span>       <span class="n">sprintf</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dest</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;%.*s&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">w</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">d</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">);</span>
  
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">dest</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
