<div class="comment" id="comment4210">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/418/" target="_top">mad</a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/4210/">#4210</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/11/18 20:37 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/11/18 20:37 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20090317033045/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/haskell/">
	  Haskell
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #dfffdf;">2/2=1.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>Haskellらしく無限リストと高階関数で。

1. 文字列の右に無限個の空白を連結
2. 左側を揃える
3. 幅の分だけ切り取る</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
